<p>ANYTHING that will reduce the probability of encounters with the police is a good thing; the less cause they have to search me/you, the better everything is. I also believe along that direction that there are currently too many excuses available that permit police searches, and that any effort to reduce the perniciousness of these is a step in the right direction.</p>
<p>Maybe next we can eliminate the stupid asset-forfeiture laws related to the use of anything someone wants to say is illegal.</p>
